#####################################################################
# Global Git Ignore Template
#
# This file contains user-specific ignore patterns that should NOT be
# in the project's .gitignore file. These are personal development
# environment preferences.
#
# To use this file:
# 1. Copy this file to your home directory: cp .gitignore_global.example ~/.gitignore_global
# 2. Configure git to use it: git config --global core.excludesfile ~/.gitignore_global
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/ignoring-files#configuring-ignored-files-for-all-repositories-on-your-computer
